T1  - Efficient Repeated Implementation
AU  - Lee, Jihong
AU  - Sabourian, Hamid
Y1  - 2011/11/01
PY  - 2011
DA  - 2011/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA8859
T2  - Econometrica
